      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BUBBLE COASTER (1) stalked the lead from a low draw then burst clear to score (19.81) at this track in a TG1-4W over 342m. Has good early burn and is suited drawn on the inside. Can continue on her winning ways. RICO CAPPUCCINO (2) returns from a three-and-a-half months break after failing to finish at this track last time but prior to that was a 19.89 winner here in a TG1-4W. Bold showing expected on best. INTEGRATOR (7) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (20.22) at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Cannot be underestimated. TIME OF DESIGN (8) generally performs well over this distance.",
